</header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><p>I am/have been fortunate to advise and learn from those listed below.</p>
<h3><strong>phd students</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>Xuanzhou (Lorraine) Chen</li>
<li><a href="https://sites.google.com/view/mengqi-lou" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mengqi Lou</a></li>
<li><a href="https://mnakul101.github.io/site/">Milind Nakul</a></li>
<li><a href="https://jyotishkarc.github.io/">Jyotishka Ray Choudhury</a></li>
</ul>
<h3><strong>alumni</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://tli432.github.io/">Tianjiao Li</a> (PhD, now postdoc at MIT)</li>
<li><a href="https://liwei-jiang97.github.io/">Liwei Jiang</a> (Postdoc, now at Purdue)</li>
